====奧斯卡颁奖乌龙事件====
在奧斯卡典禮期間，頒獎人[[費·唐娜薇|-{zh-cn:菲·唐娜薇; zh-hk:菲·丹娜惠; zh-tw:費·唐娜薇;}-]]在閲讀[[沃伦·比蒂|-{zh-hans:沃伦·比蒂;zh-hant:華倫·比提;}-]]打開的卡片之後錯誤地宣佈《樂來越愛你》贏得最佳影片，而其實它是宣佈艾瑪·史東贏得最佳女主角的複製卡片<ref>{{cite news|last=Donnelly|first=Jim|title=Moonlight Wins Best Picture After 2017 Oscars Envelope Mishap|url=http://oscar.go.com/news/winners/after-oscars-2017-mishap-moonlight-wins-best-picture|publisher=[[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|date=2017-02-26|accessdate=2017-02-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Foscar.go.com%2Fnews%2Fwinners%2Fafter-oscars-2017-mishap-moonlight-wins-best-picture%7Cpublisher%3D%5B%5BAcademy+of+Motion+Picture+Arts+and+Sciences%5D%5D%7Cdate%3DFebruary+26%2C+2017&date=2018-06-23|archive-date=2018-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《樂來越愛你》的演員和工作人員上台之後，花了兩分鐘和將近三場得獎感言秀場製作人才來糾正錯誤，而真正贏家是《[[月光男孩|-{zh-hk:月亮喜歡藍; zh-tw:月光下的藍色男孩; zh-cn:月光男孩;}-]]》<ref>{{cite news|last=Rothman|first=Michael|title='Moonlight' wins best picture after 'La La Land' mistakenly announced|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/moonlight-wins-best-picture-mistake-presenter-warren-beatty/story?id=45769592|publisher=ABC News|date=2017-02-26|accessdate=2017-02-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FEntertainment%2Fmoonlight-wins-best-picture-mistake-presenter-warren-beatty%2Fstory%3Fid%3D45769592&date=2018-06-23|archive-date=2018-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====德國電視節目惡作劇====
2017年3月，《樂來越愛你》成為德國年度影視獎{{tsl|en|Goldene Kamera|金牌攝影機獎}}的[[惡作劇|惡作劇]]焦點。德國喜劇人{{tsl|en|Joko Winterscheidt|傑可·溫特沙伊特}}和{{tsl|en|Klaas Heufer-Umlauf|克拉斯·海佛-烏諾夫}}在《樂來越愛你》贏得「最佳國際電影」獎時安排假冒瑞恩·高斯林的人來授獎<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/entertainment/movies/goslinggate-is-this-the-greatest-tv-prank-ever-20170309-guu52p.html|title=#GoslingGate: is this the greatest TV prank ever?|date=2017-03-09|work=Brisbane Times|last=Moran|first=Rob|accessdate=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170311221454/https://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/entertainment/movies/goslinggate-is-this-the-greatest-tv-prank-ever-20170309-guu52p.html|archive-date=2017-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|url=https://www.brainstain.co.uk/2017/03/08/goslinggate-golden-camera-awards-germany/|title=#GoslingGate at The Golden Camera Awards in Germany|website=brainstain.co.uk|date=2017-03-08|access-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214074533/https://www.brainstain.co.uk/2017/03/08/goslinggate-golden-camera-awards-germany/|archive-date=2017-12-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/story-behind-ryan-gosling-german-awards-show-prank-984529|title=How Two German Comedians Pranked an Awards Show With a Fake Ryan Gosling|website=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2017-03-08|access-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308223738/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/story-behind-ryan-gosling-german-awards-show-prank-984529|archive-date=2017-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典禮後，電視廣播公司[[德國電視二台|德國電視二台]]的發言人被問到獎項是否歸還時表示《樂來越愛你》已經獲獎，而獎座也會給真正的瑞恩·高斯林<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://rp-online.de/panorama/fernsehen/goldene-kamera-2017-veranstalter-fordern-trophaee-zurueck_aid-17755893|title=Goldene Kamera 2017: Veranstalter fordern Trophäe zurück|trans-title=Goldene Kamera 2017: Organizer reclaims trophy|work=Rheinische Post|date=2017-03-07|access-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213214108/https://rp-online.de/panorama/fernsehen/goldene-kamera-2017-veranstalter-fordern-trophaee-zurueck_aid-17755893|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該事件被稱為「高斯林門」，並引發了對其概念的批評。媒體影評人認為「最佳國際電影」成立目的只是讓瑞恩·高斯林出現在典禮上，而非考量電影的品質。這件事也成為2019年金牌攝影機獎遭到取消的導火線<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dwdl.de/nachrichten/73880/miese_quote_mieser_ruf_aus_fuer_goldene_kamera/|title=Miese Quote, mieser Ruf: Aus für Goldene Kamera|trans-title=Bad ratings, bad reputation: The end for Goldene Kamera|date=September 5, 2019|first=Thomas|last=Lückerath|website=dwdl.de|access-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213215453/https://www.dwdl.de/nachrichten/73880/miese_quote_mieser_ruf_aus_fuer_goldene_kamera/?utm_source=&utm_medium=&utm_campaign=&utm_term=|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|url=http://www.quotenmeter.de/n/115772/sendetermin-fuer-die-letzte-goldene-kamera-steht|website=quotenmeter.de|title=Sendetermin für die letzte "Goldene Kamera" steht|trans-title=Air date for the final "Goldene Kamera" announced|date=2020-02-11|access-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213221027/http://www.quotenmeter.de/n/115772/sendetermin-fuer-die-letzte-goldene-kamera-steht|archive-date=2020-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，溫特沙伊特和海佛-烏諾夫因遭到[[媒體研究|媒體批評]]而贏得{{tsl|en|Grimme Award|格力莫獎}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.stern.de/kultur/grimme-preis-der-falsche-ryan-gosling-wird-ausgezeichnet-7900918.html|website=Stern|date=2018-03-14|title=Grimme-Preis: Der falsche Ryan Gosling wird ausgezeichnet|trans-title=Grimme Award: The false Ryan Gosling will be awarded|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314211907/https://www.stern.de/kultur/grimme-preis-der-falsche-ryan-gosling-wird-ausgezeichnet-7900918.html|archive-date=2018-03-14|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref>。

